body:
Here are some suggestions: -

(1) `ValueError: Tried to convert 'x' to a tensor and failed. Error: None values not supported.` which implies the value of `x` used in first line of your code `y = tf.to_int32(x)` is missing.

(2) Please review guidelines for raising an issue here. [https://github.com/printdhruv/tensorflow/blob/master/ISSUE_TEMPLATE.md](https://github.com/printdhruv/tensorflow/blob/master/ISSUE_TEMPLATE.md)
